# Gate-scope secrets — injected ONLY into the deterministic gate checks (which run your
# tests — NOT Claude), so the acceptance suite can use secrets no Claude process ever sees.
# Lives as PLAINTEXT secret.gate.env in the workspace (gitignored — never commit it).
# Prefer disposable / test-scoped values.
#
# Examples (replace with yours):
# DATABASE_URL=postgres://test:test@db.test.local:5432/app_test
# STRIPE_TEST_KEY=sk_test_xxxxxxxx
# TEST_API_TOKEN=xxxxxxxx
